room_title: Escape room "John Hayden's Room" by 13th Hour Haunted House in New York
room_description: Are you brave enough to enter the Hayden House where the walls echo desperate screams and are red with the blood of countless murders? Your task is to find out who will be John Hayden's next victim. For years, the Hayden case has remained unsolved. Will you join the souls who've met their death here?
